== 用法 ==
See [[Template_talk:Infobox play|this template's talk page]] for more information about using this template in articles about [[Play (theatre)|Play]]s.

To use the template, copy the following into an article and fill in the appropriate sections. There is no need to delete unwanted sections.

All fields are optional.

